'''大卫·史威默'''（{{lang-en|David Schwimmer}}，{{bd|1966年|11月2日|||}}）是一位美国[[猶太|猶太]]裔电视电影演员、导演<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/id/3080030/ns/dateline_nbc-newsmakers/t/schwimmers-serious-side/#.WwKtJO6FOUk|title=David Schwimmer's serious side|accessdate=May 21, 2018|author=|date=November 21, 2003|work=NBC News|publisher=|quote=David Schwimmer: "And when it comes to certain prejudice and the hatred that still pervades this country I'm a Jew first and not a white person."|archive-date=2020-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200405200931/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/3080030/ns/dateline_nbc-newsmakers/t/schwimmers-serious-side/#.WwKtJO6FOUk|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.salon.com/2016/05/27/david_schwimmer_puts_in_the_work_on_learning_wine_waiting_tables_and_why_he_campaigned_for_years_for_a_black_girlfriend_for_ross_geller/|script-title=en:David Schwimmer puts in the work: On learning wine, waiting tables and why he “campaigned for years for a black girlfriend” for Ross Geller|accessdate=May 21, 2018|author=|date=May 27, 2016|last=Saraiya|first=Sonia|work=Salon|publisher=|quote=David Schwimmer: "Yes, I was Jewish"|archive-date=2021-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304105742/https://www.salon.com/2016/05/27/david_schwimmer_puts_in_the_work_on_learning_wine_waiting_tables_and_why_he_campaigned_for_years_for_a_black_girlfriend_for_ross_geller/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Shiryn|last=Solny|url=https://www.algemeiner.com/2018/02/15/mayor-rahm-emanuel-actor-david-schwimmer-bond-over-having-critical-jewish-mothers/|title=Mayor Rahm Emanuel, Actor David Schwimmer Bond Over Having Critical Jewish Mothers|work=Algemeiner|date=February 15, 2018|accessdate=May 21, 2018|archive-date=2020-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202190430/https://www.algemeiner.com/2018/02/15/mayor-rahm-emanuel-actor-david-schwimmer-bond-over-having-critical-jewish-mothers/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Nate|last=Bloom|url=https://www.interfaithfamily.com/arts_and_entertainment/popular_culture/interfaith_celebrities_the_talks_hosts_and_david_schwimmers_bride/|title=Interfaith Celebrities: The Talk’s Hosts and David Schwimmers Bride|work=InterfaithFamily.com|date=October 26, 2010|accessdate=May 21, 2018|archive-date=2019-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190801013005/https://www.interfaithfamily.com/arts_and_entertainment/popular_culture/interfaith_celebrities_the_talks_hosts_and_david_schwimmers_bride/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1966年生于纽约，2岁后移居洛杉矶<ref name="hello">{{cite web|url=http://www.hellomagazine.com/profiles/davidschwimmer/|title=Hello Magazine Profile - David Schwimmer|work=[[Hello|Hello!]]|publisher=''hellomagazine.com''|accessdate=2009-03-29|language=en|archive-date=2009-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090604140601/http://hellomagazine.com/profiles/davidschwimmer/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="yahoo">{{cite web|url=http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/contributor/1800024595/bio|title=David Schwimmer Biography|publisher=[[雅虎|Yahoo!]]|accessdate=2009-03-29|language=en|archive-date=2009-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091205030602/http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/contributor/1800024595/bio|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。1988年毕业于[[西北大学_(美国伊利诺州)|西北大学]]，获得文学学士。毕业后混迹于洛杉矶，在一些影视剧中充当龙套，四处赶场寻找演出机会<ref name="yahoo"/>。

1989年在电视电影剧''A Deadly Silence''中担纲角色。此后开始在一系列电视剧中饰演配角：''L.A. Law''、''The Wonder Years''、''NYPD Blue''以及1990年代初的''Monty''。不久，史威默凭借[[情景喜剧|情景喜剧]]《[[老友记|老友记]]》以及自己饰演的[[羅斯·蓋勒|羅斯·蓋勒]]一角大获成功，并且在全世界获得广泛影响力，1995年，他因《六人行》中的罗斯角色而获得[[艾美奖|艾美奖]]提名。此后史威默也开始进军电影界，1996年在《[[出殡抱佳人|出殡抱佳人]]》中首次出演。此后在《[[吻着傻情人|吻着傻情人]]》（Kissing a Fool，1998）、《[[六天七夜|六天七夜]]》（Six Days, Seven Nights, 1998）、《[[纳粹追凶|纳粹追凶]]》（Apt Pupil，2000）和《[[拣起碎片|拣起碎片]]》（Picking Up the Pieces，2000）中先后客串。 

2001年，他在电视剧《[[諾曼第大空降|諾曼第大空降]]》中饰演严苛且不受士兵喜欢的賀伯特·索伯一角。尽管遭到影评嘲讽<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/1544232.stm|title=Band of Brothers impresses|last=Hill|first=Aubrey|date=September 14, 2001|work=[[英國廣播公司新聞|BBC News]]|publisher=[[英国广播公司|BBC]]|accessdate=2009-03-29|quote=Part of the problem... may have been the ridiculous fact that ''Friends'' favourite David Schwimmer plays the hard and cruel Captain Herbert Sobel. The only thing believable about Schwimmer's acting is when he cowers in the face of true battle. His puppy dog eyes make him appear even more pitiful.|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225190033/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/1544232.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但依然依靠在该剧中的表演获得2002年美国卫星奖影视系列剧最佳男配角<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0001710/awards|title=Awards for David Schwimmer|publisher=[[互联网电影数据库|IMDB]]|accessdate=2009-03-29|language=en|archive-date=2018-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180219090305/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0001710/awards|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

